nodes.text: A Falleen monk who operated out of an Equilibrate chapel at a Wayfarer's Temple in Falleen Throne, the capital city of the planet Falleen, also acted as an agent of the Rebel Alliance. When the holostar and Rebel agent Javul Charn visited Falleen as part of a galactic tour, the monk provided her with a data wafer containing updated orders and codes to access a container she was to pick for the Alliance while performing on Bannistar Station.
